## Phase 3 — Wire git post-merge hook

- [ ] If `{{PROJECT_ROOT}}/.git/` exists:
  - Write to `{{PROJECT_ROOT}}/.git/hooks/post-merge`:
    ```
    #!/bin/bash
    exec "{{PLUGIN_PATH}}/hooks/post-merge.sh" "$@"
    ```
  - Run: `chmod +x {{PROJECT_ROOT}}/.git/hooks/post-merge`
- [ ] If not a git repo:
  - Print warning: "Not a git repository. Post-merge ingest will not work until you run `git init` then `/llake-doctor`."
  - Do NOT fail the plan
- [ ] **Append to `{{PROJECT_ROOT}}/llake/log.md`:**
  ```
  ## [{{DATE}}] install-plan | Phase 3 complete: post-merge wired (or deferred)
  ```

## Phase 4 — Register Claude Code hooks (global)

- [ ] Read `~/.claude/settings.json` (create with `{}` if missing)
