- [ ] Ensure the `hooks.SessionEnd` array contains an entry pointing at `{{PLUGIN_PATH}}/hooks/session-end.sh`. If not present, add it.
- [ ] Write the updated settings file.
- [ ] **Append to `{{PROJECT_ROOT}}/llake/log.md`:**
  ```
  ## [{{DATE}}] install-plan | Phase 4 complete: CC hooks registered
  ```

